ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 197, Alberta
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 197 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of ALBERTA, with respect to the SEVERE WILDFIRES, that affected the province on May 2016.
